Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這髮型都一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我女兒的意見… 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}挺適合…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說是這一點都不適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天我就改回原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}無論怎樣嘗試 不行的事情就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和現在日本的體操界一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}25年前在蒙特婁奧運獲得團體金牌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之後再也沒有出過成績
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也沒辦法怪別人不關注我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你獲得個人獎牌的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家熱鬧得不行 都說你的髮型像武士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}現在就這麼對你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,0:01:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我換成那種髮型的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}問題不在這好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒出成績是教練的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想要推行全新的指導方式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也只有在新一代的年輕人身上嘗試了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也覺得對不起你們這一代人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不足的部分就靠練習來彌補
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是 得趕快為下次比賽制定練習計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的肩膀痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即便是堅持負傷參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}未來你依舊沒有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}退役吧 城太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你應該清楚感受到身體的極限…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等…稍等…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以 你接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是爸爸我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是玲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}牛奶喝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爸爸要喝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去買點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就沒事了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她說家裡牛奶沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以你現在的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}繼續堅持也不會有結果了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一定會後悔 家人也會為你傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今後就別再專注體操 多照顧一下小玲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不適合做教練
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}考慮一下自己的出路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是怎麼能突然就退役…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已經說了好幾年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}城太郎 差不多該考慮一下自己的將來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我會繼續大展身手的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不如把位置讓給年輕人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是 得讓他們活動活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是時候脫下運動服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是 出了不少汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也不好 看你那樣沒好意思點透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我應該更直截了當一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的是對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}退役嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}退役?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}退役…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}完全無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天草先生怎麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}接下來是NHK杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們沒有討論參賽前的計劃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個計劃可真是前所未有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}挺厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吃吧 BigBird
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}退役吧 城太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}退役…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爸爸累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看爸爸今天一直發呆 可能是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}肩膀沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這次寒假我們去看忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:04:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知世 天草先生讓我退役…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果作為選手 無法照顧好玲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我就結束選手生涯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自從妳走了以後 這是我第一次和玲旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我決定在那時告訴玲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過我還是覺得我不需要退役…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你和媽媽新婚旅行的時候去過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是為什麼是鬼怒川呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為有江戶村嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還有溫泉和索道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}鬼怒川可有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還希望藉此機會能住到同一家旅店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒想到竟然倒閉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳還真是喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}帥呆了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在「大奧VS女忍」中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:38.36,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}註：「大奧」指江戶城中最深處女性居室的部分，也是將軍後宮的稱呼。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母親扮演的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}躲開女官般若的機關槍的那一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}動作比基努都要靈活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:44.65,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}註：基努·李維，加拿大男演員、導演、製片人和音樂家，代表作品有「駭客任務」等。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還是看到爸爸以後 我才喜歡上忍者的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}體操不就像忍者一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爸爸 趕快趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果發現了可疑的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就把十手指向他 這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.37,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}註：十手，一種武器兼捕具。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「哪裡跑」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把我當成可疑的傢伙練習一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}準備 一 二…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪裡跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所謂忍者 即為遵守規則之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:34.70,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}當時有一名質疑規則的忍者離開了故鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}四點就停業了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個節目結束就告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK_准\c&HFBFEFD&\3c&H3A3552&\pos(640,611)}找到你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord1\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK_准\c&HFBFEFD&\3c&H3A3552&\pos(640,714)}Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}特工出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是史密斯 史密斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是表演嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Yamakasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.28,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}註：「Yamakasi」，法國跑酷運動團隊。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玲…玲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:41.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玲!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 玲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忍者!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}髮髻喵!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:31.64,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}註：「ニャンまげ」，該主題公園的吉祥物。
