Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪裡跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\pos(639.00,657.00)\blur2\fsp0.4\fs32\fnSitka Small\b1)\i1}Bravo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好哇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江戶村也變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}完全錯過了機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她也長大了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}聽我說 玲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}說不出話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}鬼怒川好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好玩極了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是嗎 太好…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回家了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奶奶好像不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯? 哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我回來了 BigBird
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}背後是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}背後?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你再說些怪話 就把你送回南美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去打開洗衣機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用 我去就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}差點就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得趕快告訴她我要退役的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}浴缸裡有個忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:11:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爸爸 他是我們在江戶村遇到的忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對對 江戶村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是不是 所以說你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下是叛逃忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正被特工追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果被抓住就要被送回國了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸? 之前那不是表演嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}特工又是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}BigBird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下想留在日本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請讓在下留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他好像不是什麼壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他擅自跑進我們家 還不是壞人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奶奶!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奶奶 忍者忍者忍者!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:53.13,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他從江戶村跟著來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不是日本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忍法·跪拜術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}開玩笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下想留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下不想被強制遣返
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}隨你便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你有你的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你這種傢伙 池袋有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那也沒有忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在「大奧VS女忍」中 浪人也保護了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}媽媽可以 這傢伙不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是我搭建起來的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣在下就可以繼續做忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個忍者真的要住下了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都怪他 我又沒能說出退役的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天休息 是直接去俱樂部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玲也一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能留妳和這忍者在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯? 在下?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦 是小玲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}瀧澤!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}城太郎先生 難得休一次假 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好放鬆了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們去了鬼怒川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的? 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}鬼生氣的河川 鬼怒川?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}見到鬼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒見到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的嗎 竟然沒見到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒有鬼是不是不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明明叫鬼怒川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過我們見到忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}騙人吧 忍者?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忍者好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:56.51,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就不該叫鬼怒川了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他不就在我們家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:59.76,Dialogue_Alt,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忍…忍怒川?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有話和天草先生說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以先做完熱身運動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你還沒告訴她?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已經好幾次想告訴她了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你倒是說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我沒做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下週的見面會可是改不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然今天小玲來了 你就找機會告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好標準
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼樣才能做到筆直
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣用力然後這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}表演一下別的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 小傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}城太郎先生受傷 你們該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}別麻煩他喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我們什麼時候能再看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}城太郎先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其實我準備退…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗨! Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下來幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎麼跑到這來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他又跟來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小玲 忍怒川!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來池袋也有忍怒川!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}池…忍袋?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忍者?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上陣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等…你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個忍者可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這次是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼樣 我厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我做得不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}從昨天開始 你怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下隨時準備幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下還想看到你的體操
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}還? 你一次都沒看過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}名叫里安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}里安?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 武士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這就到了見面會當天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每次我想開口 那個忍者都會搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少在走出家門之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爸爸真帥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玲 爸爸今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:19:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Joe! 帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要去聚會嗎 什麼聚會?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好厲害 好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底是什麼聚會?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}BB 閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 天草先生還等著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下 玲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去吧 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒事的 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玲 Joe這是要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}體操就是我的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而我也僅僅懂得體操
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即便如我 也娶到了一位出色的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們有了一個女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是一位很好的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女兒曾說過喜歡看我的體操表演
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我認為 成家之後體操依舊支撐著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而我作為一名體操選手走到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這次我做出了一個決定…
